        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/skunk/scene_skunk.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository ee27bfd3-e0a1-405e-a4f8-eb5f58ebfee3).Image",
        "Description": "To: our contractor-\r\rThe Don&apos;s patience ran dry. That politician&apos;s got plans that are gonna mess with our business, his buddy&apos;s been pulling strings, and Cervantez tipped the cops that we&apos;re watching. That&apos;s three problems, one solution. Handle it quiet, and clean. No press. When they&apos;re gone, the noise dies with &apos;em. You&apos;ll be paid when the city forgets their names.  \r\r-Carlo",
